snippet.title: T.E.C. 3001 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/t.e.c-3001/id698189340?mt=8

XBOX 360 Marketplace: http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-GB/Product/TEC-3001/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d8025855093b

http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-GB/Product/TEC-3001/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d8025855093b

T.E.C. is 3D action single player indie game for XBOX.  You are guiding a robot through a virtual space to collect leftovers of energy for human kind.
